### Blitz Backend API Requests
### Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
# Once you login, replace the token below with your actual accessToken
@authToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ==========================================
### 1. SYSTEM
### ==========================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz

### ==========================================
### 2. AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fullName": "Umar Samandarov",
    "phoneNumber": "+998901234567",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phoneNumber": "+998901234567",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### ==========================================
### 3. DRIVERS
### ==========================================

### Create Driver
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "full_name": "Akmal Karimov",
    "phone": "+998911112233",
    "license_number": "AB1234567",
    "car_model": "Chevrolet Cobalt",
    "car_plate": "01A123BC",
    "status": "active"
}

### List Drivers (Pagination & Filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers?page=1&limit=10&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Search Drivers (by Name or Phone)
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers?search=Akmal
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Driver by ID
# Replace ID with an actual driver ID from the list response
@driverId = YOUR_DRIVER_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Driver Info
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "car_model": "Chevrolet Tracker",
    "phone": "+998911112244"
}

### Update Driver Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "status": "blocked"
}

### Delete Driver (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/drivers/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ==========================================
### 4. STATISTICS (MENING G'OYAM)
### ==========================================

### Get Active Drivers Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/stats/active?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Blocked Drivers Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/drivers/stats/active?status=blocked
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
